# Merglbot â€” Cursor ignore list (security + performance)
#
# Cursor blocks access to these files from Agent/Tab/Semantic search.
# This is best-effort protection; still follow MERGLBOT_AI_TOOLS.md and never paste secrets into prompts.
#
# Syntax: same as .gitignore

# Secrets / env
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
**/*.env.*

# Common credentials / keys
**/credentials.json
**/secrets.json
**/secrets/**
**/*secret*
!**/*secret*.md
!**/*secret*.mdx
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa
**/id_dsa
**/id_ecdsa
**/id_ed25519
**/*service-account*.json
**/*sa-key*.json

# Package manager / CLI auth files
**/.npmrc
**/.pypirc
**/.netrc
**/.docker/config.json

# Cloud CLI creds (if copied into repo/workspace)
**/application_default_credentials.json
**/.aws/credentials
**/.aws/config
**/.config/gcloud/**

# Terraform sensitive inputs/state
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json
**/.terraform/**
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*

# Local caches / build outputs (reduce noise)
**/node_modules/**
**/.next/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.cache/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/.venv/**
**/.pytest_cache/**
